title: Hlavackova-Hradecka v Barty-Dellacqua US Open 2013 Doubles Final
description:
WTA US Open, 2013.

Doubles Final, Andrea Hlavackova/Lucie Hradecka vs Ashleigh Barty/Casey Dellacqua, recording of US Open live stream.

Transcoded from MPEG-2 720p/25 at 8 Mbps by ffmpeg using settings -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -preset veryfast -tune animation -c:a libfdk_aac -ab 64000.

Some points were missed at the start of games when the stream had to be restarted after lag set in.
